# FinTrack AI — Cursor Rules
# AI assistant context for this codebase. Read before making any changes.
# Last updated: March 2026 (v1.3)

---

## 1. Project Context

FinTrack AI is a **personal finance management web application** targeting Vietnamese millennials.
It features AI-powered transaction recording via natural language, budget tracking with color alerts,
investment portfolio management, and financial reports.

**Full documentation is in `docs/ai/`:**
- `docs/ai/architecture.md`  — System architecture, domain modules, data flow
- `docs/ai/conventions.md`   — Naming conventions, coding patterns, anti-patterns
- `docs/ai/data-model.md`    — All 9 database tables with column types and relationships
- `docs/ai/known-issues.md`  — Active bugs with root causes and exact fixes needed

**Always read the relevant docs/ai/ file before modifying a domain.**

