## 6. Shared Utilities

**Date utilities** — `shared/date/index.ts`:
```typescript
import { todayString, formatDate, getCurrentMonthYear, monthPrefix, daysBetween } from "@shared/date";
// OR from server:
import { todayString } from "../shared/date";
```

**Currency utilities** — `shared/currency/index.ts`:
```typescript
import { formatVND, formatCompact, parseMoneyText, getBudgetProgressColor, calcSimpleInterest } from "@shared/currency";
// OR from server:
import { formatVND } from "../shared/currency";
```

**Legacy utilities** — `client/src/lib/utils.ts`:
```typescript
import { cn, formatVND, getBudgetProgressColor } from "@/lib/utils";
// Still works — kept for backward compatibility
```

